OL,2,MMarine Energy: Electronics overboard!
OL,4,CThomas Lake
OL,5,CFri 12:20-12:50
OL,6,CStage B
OL,8,GThere's no shortage of power in the
OL,9,Gmarine environment, but how do we turn
OL,10,Git into something we can use? And how
OL,11,Gcan we measure what's happening in
OL,12,Gthis energetic environment when water
OL,13,Gand electronics generally shouldn't be
OL,14,Gmixed? A quick tour of wave and tidal
OL,15,Gpower, and how we can measure the
OL,16,Gpower available at sea - including
OL,17,Gsome examples of how that works (or
OL,18,Gdoesn't) in practice from prototype
OL,19,Gtesting and research. Featuring
OL,20,Gspecialised instrumentation with a
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
